      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R2 is a commercially distributed, FDA-recognized solver. Regression test suite (1,847 cases) passed at 98.2%. Version control via Git with locked release tag v2023R2-ortho. All three analysts hold current ANSYS certification. Configuration management records archived in institutional QMS. Achieved Gradation 3 exceeds MRL 3 requirement of Gradation 2."
