      },
      "rationale": "Three benchmark problems executed: lid-driven cavity (Re=100: 0.31% error; Re=1000: 0.78% error), Poiseuille flow (0.18% error), and Carreau-fluid channel (1.43% error). All within acceptance thresholds. Benchmark reports archived as DOC-NCV-2024-001 through DOC-NCV-2024-003. Achieves required Gradation 2."
