        "description": "Mean absolute percentage error (MAPE) in RAI across all five gait phases must be < 10%. At least 80% of spatial particle-concentration predictions must fall within experimental uncertainty bounds (±1 standard deviation of replicate measurements). Systematic bias must be < 5%."
